&lt;b&gt;weighted FWHM&lt;/b&gt;: this is an improvement of a simple FWHM. It allows to exclude much more spurious images by using the number of stars detected compared to the reference image (star-based registration only)

&lt;b&gt;roundness&lt;/b&gt;: images with best star roundness (star-based registration only)

