                                          <item translatable="yes">minimum</item>
                                          <item translatable="yes">center of gravity</item>
                                        </items>
                                      </object>
                                    </property>
                                    <property name="tooltip-text" translatable="1">Specifies the framing method to be used:
- "current" uses the current reference image
- "maximum" (bounding box) adds a black border around each image as required so that no part of the image is cropped when registered.
- "minimum" (common area) crops each image to the area it has in common with all images of the sequence.
- "center of gravity" determines the best framing position as the center of gravity (cog) of all the images</property>
                                    <property name="valign">center</property>
                                    <property name="hexpand">1</property>
